Interface SlimefunGuideImplementation

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BookSlimefunGuide, CheatSheetSlimefunGuide, ChestSlimefunGuide

    public interface SlimefunGuideImplementation
    This interface is used for the different implementations that add behaviour to the SlimefunGuide.
